OL,3,CBirmingham City Council pays itself
OL,4,Calmost #500,000 in charges and fines
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council has paid more
OL,7,Fthan #470,000 to itself in charges and
OL,8,Ffines because its own vehicles break
OL,9,Fthe rules of the organisation's own
OL,10,FClean Air Zone (CAZ) which aims to
OL,11,Ftackle city centre pollution.
OL,13,FBefore the CAZ was introduced, the
OL,14,Fcouncil said air pollution was
OL,15,Fresponsible for shortening the lives
OL,16,Fof about 900 people per year.
OL,18,FIts aim was to reduce the most harmful
OL,19,Fair pollutants - nitrogen dioxide and
OL,20,Fparticulate matter.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
