OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779991869
OL,3,CBirmingham City Council pays itself
OL,4,Calmost #500,000 in charges and fines
OL,6,FIt says that many of those vehicles
OL,7,Fare minibuses related to social
OL,8,Fservices and education provision.
OL,10,FGovernment commissioners have been
OL,11,Fworking with Birmingham City Council
OL,12,Fsince it issued a so-called Section
OL,13,F114 notice in 2023 ` often referred to
OL,14,Fas declaring its own effective
OL,15,Fbankruptcy.
OL,17,FIn March, its then-Labour leadership
OL,18,Fhailed its first balanced budget in
OL,19,Fthree years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
