PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779991869
OL,3,CBirmingham City Council pays itself
OL,4,Calmost #500,000 in charges and fines
OL,6,FThe income from CAZ charges and fines
OL,7,Fgoes towards the operating costs of
OL,8,Fthe scheme and any surplus has to be
OL,9,Fspent on transport or environmental
OL,10,Fschemes. The money does not go back
OL,11,Finto the council's general funds so it
OL,12,Fcannot be reallocated to other
OL,13,Fprojects.
OL,15,FThe Shared Data Unit found the number
OL,16,Fof fines and daily charges paid by
OL,17,FBirmingham City Council represented
OL,18,Faround 20 times the number of those
OL,19,Fpaid by any other UK council running a
OL,20,FCAZ, Low Emission Zone (LEZ) or Ultra
OL,21,FLow Emission Zone (ULEZ).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
