OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779991869
OL,3,CBirmingham City Council pays itself
OL,4,Calmost #500,000 in charges and fines
OL,6,FUnder the CAZ scheme, the daily charge
OL,7,Ffor vehicles that do not meet emission
OL,8,Fstandards is #8 for cars, vans and
OL,9,Ftaxis or #50 for HGVs and coaches,
OL,10,Funless a valid exemption is in place.
OL,12,FBirmingham City Council does not offer
OL,13,Fany specific exemptions to council
OL,14,Fvehicles, nor those used by its
OL,15,Fcontractors.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
